# ------------------------------------------------------------
# GridLock AES: Source-First .gitignore
# Optimized for Xilinx Vivado SystemVerilog Projects
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# --- SECTION 1: Ignore Massive Vivado Junk ---
# These folders contain gigabytes of temporary bitstreams and logs
.Xil/
*.cache/
*.hw/
*.ip_user_files/
*.runs/
*.sim/
*.data/
xsim.dir/

# --- SECTION 2: Ignore Individual Temporary Files ---
*.jou
*.log
*.pb
*.str
*.os
*.o
*.obj
vivado_*.backup.*
*.tclbackup

# --- SECTION 3: System & IDE Bloat ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
Thumbs.db

# --- SECTION 4: THE SAFETY NET (The Whitelist) ---
# This ensures Git NEVER ignores your actual code, even if it's 
# inside one of the folders ignored above.

!*.v
!*.sv
!*.vh
!*.svh
!*.xdc
!*.xpr
!*.tcl
!*.md
!LICENSE
!.gitignore

# Also specifically allow the source directory if it exists
!**/srcs/
!**/rtl/
!**/tb/
